     SHORT="Free, open source, cross-platform audio editor"

cat << EOF
Audacity is a free, open source, cross-platform audio editor for recording,
playing, importing and exporting audio. It works with many audio formats and
allows you to record from line in, microphone or other sources.

Features include:
- Recording from line in, microphone, or other sources
- Editing with Cut, Copy, Paste functions
- Many built-in effects including reverb, echo, and equalization
- Spectrogram view for detailed audio analysis
- Easy-to-use interface
- Built-in Generate menu to create audio
- Built-in Analyze menu
EOF
